cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper discusses computer vision tasks such as semantic segmentation, human body pose estimation, and object tracking. 
2. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is likely as the paper proposes a combinatorial optimization problem and a local search algorithm to solve it. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses a mathematical abstraction of computer vision tasks and proposes a solution algorithm. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is possible as the paper proposes a generalization of two NP-hard problems and offers a feasible solution algorithm. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also possible as the paper discusses a combinatorial optimization problem and proposes a solution algorithm that converges to a local optimum.
